flowchart TB
  CLI["OpenDSS command interface\n(.dss scripts)"] --> Engine["OpenDSS Engine\n(circuit model + solver)"]
  Engine --> Solve["Solve (snapshot / time-series / harmonic modes)"]
  Solve --> Results["Results:\nBus voltages (per-phase)\nElement powers/currents\nLosses\nMonitors/Meters"]
  Results --> API["Python/COM bridge\n(OpenDSSDirect.py / COM)"]
  API --> Adapter["dt-sim-opendss adapter\n(map ↔ GridGraph)"]

